snippet.title: Dark Continent: Mist Gameplay Android / iOS Fantasy MMORPG
snippet.description:
Dark Continent: Mist by EYOUGAME(USS) is a brand new fantasy MMORPG mobile game, with excellent 3D graphics and game special effects. A vast Oriental-style fantasy world, with a rich combat system, allows players to experience various game modes.
Darkness awakens, and fog spreads across the continent; Incarnate gods and demons, awaken ancient powers; Bloody battle, keep the last hope!

🔋Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.eyougame.ynxxsy
🍎iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id6444000640
- Total Size: 837 MB
- Apk Size: 325 MB
🌏 Network: Online
★ Play on PC: https://bit.ly/3B51crR
